OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774275077
OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,FShildon has been named as the most
OL,7,Faffordable town in Britain for
OL,8,Ffamilies looking to buy a home.
OL,10,FZoopla, which carried out the
OL,11,Fresearch, compared average prices for
OL,12,Fthree-bedroom homes with estimated
OL,13,Fearnings for couples working full-time.
OL,15,FTowns in northern England, Scotland
OL,16,Fand Wales dominated the top of the
OL,17,Faffordability rankings, which were
OL,18,Fbased on 300 towns that are popular
OL,19,Fwith people looking to buy family-
OL,20,Fsized homes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
