OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774275077
OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,FShildon, in County Durham, topped the
OL,7,Flist with an average house price-to-
OL,8,Fearnings ratio of 1.36. It was one of
OL,9,Fsix towns in the North East which made
OL,10,Fthe top 10.
OL,12,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,13,FZoopla, said: "The housing market is
OL,14,Fentering one of its busiest periods,
OL,15,Fwith the most homes for sale in many
OL,16,Fyears and at a time when buyers are
OL,17,Fbecoming increasingly focused on value
OL,18,Ffor money.
OL,26,@uD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774275077
OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,F"What stands out is the scale of the
OL,7,Faffordability gap across the UK. In
OL,8,Fparts of the North East, families can
OL,9,Fbuy a home for much less than the cost
OL,10,Fof buying in the most affordable towns
OL,11,Fin southern England.
OL,13,F"While there are affordable options in
OL,14,Fevery region, buyers often face a
OL,15,Ftrade-off between lower house prices
OL,16,Fand their proximity to major
OL,17,Femployment centres.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774275077
OL,3,CRailway town named Britain's most
OL,4,Caffordable for families to buy a home
OL,6,F"Many of the most affordable towns in
OL,7,Fsouthern England are coastal, meaning
OL,8,Fbetter affordability may come at the
OL,9,Fcost of more expensive travel which
OL,10,Fmay not work for everyone."
OL,12,FIn Wales, Ferndale in the Rhondda
OL,13,FValley was named as the most
OL,14,Faffordable town for families, with
OL,15,Fhomes there costing around 1.85 times
OL,16,Fearnings.
OL,18,FIn Scotland, Cumnock in East Ayrshire
OL,19,Fwas placed top, with three-bedroom
OL,20,Fhomes costing around 1.68 times dual
OL,21,Fwages.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
